#

Slow Cooker Pork and Beans

495 min
$20
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinDairy-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Slow CookerComfort FoodHearty Meal

Description

A hearty, savory dish that combines tender pork with rich, flavorful beans for a satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • pork shoulder: 2 pounds
  • canned navy beans: 3 cans
  • onion: 1 large, chopped
  • garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • chicken broth: 2 cups
  • barbecue sauce: 1 cup
  • brown sugar: 1/4 cup
  • mustard: 2 tablespoons
  • pepper: to taste
  • salt: to taste
  • cayenne pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
